model_explanation: S1 only restricts what Rob received (just bananas), and says nothing about Tom.
if Tom only got grapes from Sam, he did not get oranges.
"only gave Sue oranges" rules out Sam giving Sue apples.
S1 limits Sue’s items (only bananas) but doesn’t say whether Rob got bananas.
if Sam only gave Tom oranges, he did not give Tom bananas.
if Sam only gave Sue apples, he did not give her oranges.
if Sam only gave Sue grapes, he did not give her apples.
"only gave Ellen oranges" means no bananas to Ellen.
if Sam only gave Mary grapes, he did not give her apples.
S1 doesn’t restrict what others received; Mary could also have gotten oranges.
